channel.title: :mermaid: Siren Ep - OffCmd [ dark electro house ]
channel.description:
During the third Auxy tournament challenges I came up with [a few ideas](https://soundcloud.com/offender/high) that then got further developed into full tracks, and today they've materialized into this 4 track EP: [https://offcmd.bandcamp.com/album/siren-ep](https://offcmd.bandcamp.com/album/siren-ep)
Very intense, deep and layered melodies. All Auxy except for the vocals on "So High" by Carol Borges. Thanks for your continued support! @DHO, @NotMiles, @paxman, @Sunny OffCmd.
